{"tid":2530884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拜登率領白宮帶頭脫口罩，共和黨參議員：終於自由了","createTime":"2021-05-14T18:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-14T19:02:14.000Z","uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"74af9c53c655e87f56e803ec11c2cac9d85c8a6e","tid":2530884,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T18:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd6CShhrbw7zueSTiV9C3KqjJ4ESQEycQqSuBhX136voG?filename=VDN0usB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVDN0usB.jpg&h=b48d9460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聯邦疾病防治中心(CDC)13日放寬接種完成者的戴口罩規範，他們在戶外人群中與多數室內場合可不戴口罩；隨後拜登總統在白宮帶頭拿下口罩，白宮幕僚與記者也跟進<br />\n<br />\n參院共和黨領袖麥康諾(Mitch McConnell)高呼「終於自由了」；第一夫人訪西維吉尼亞州時摘下口罩，還開玩笑說「感覺好赤裸。」<br />\n<br />\nCDC13日發布新指南，已完成接種的人無須戴口罩，但有少數例外；CDC主任瓦倫斯基(Rochelle Walensky)表示：「我們盼望此刻許久，我們期待可以回歸部分常態的那一刻。」<br />\n<br />\n感覺拜登都唔係咁討厭姐<br />\n最少美國人終於自由了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e076bbe55f259c621215af5165be98d518b8b711","tid":2530884,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T19:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1024/1*_eIukvwcBOu3fZ6gj0QDBw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1024%2F1%2A_eIukvwcBOu3fZ6gj0QDBw.png&h=624a131d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}